                    <lb n="1"/><persName type="divine" ref="#Apollo"><name nymRef="#Ἀπόλλων"><supplied reason="lost">Τὀπόλλōν</supplied><unclear>ό</unclear>ς</name></persName> <w lemma="εἰμι">hεμι</w>.
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>J'appartiens à Apollon.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>I belong to Apollo.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Sono proprietà di Apollo.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p>أنا أخص أبوللو أو أنا أكون ملكاً لأبوللو</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>For the spelling <foreign xml:lang="grc">ΗΕMI</foreign> (also in <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr002600</ref>), see <bibl><ptr target="#cdl2000"/>, p. <citedRange>13</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
